		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸赤鹫进行啄击、右翼翻转两段攻击，分别造成<span color="#ff9999">50%,70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家更远时，圣骸赤鹫振翅起飞，朝玩家飞过来，两翼交替施放火焰弹落地轰炸，每个火焰弹造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="431" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每45s-60s，圣骸赤鹫升空化作火球，产生并发射大量焰飞刃对准玩家，命中造成<span color="#ff9999">50%,25%,12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害，同时形成</span><span color="#dd4a04">「</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#dd4a04">噬骸能量块·火</span><span color="#dd4a04">」</span><span>；此时赤鹫失去强化抗性正常，6s后则会被赤鹫吸收恢复强化。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸赤鹫.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1268" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸赤鹫.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸赤鹫.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1392" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/圣骸赤鹫.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1392" y="651">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸赤鹫进行双啄击、左爪划、旋火龙卷三段攻击，分别造成<span color="#ff9999">50%x2,80%,<br/>100%</span><span>伤害，及时远离可以打断旋火龙卷的攻击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，圣骸赤鹫振翅起跳，在玩家处下落，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于赤鹫后方时，圣骸赤鹫瞬间转身攻击，造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1023" width="999" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">圣骸赤鹫从开局、瘫痪恢复后或者吸收<span color="#dd4a04">「噬骸能量块·火」</span><span>之后，将进行抗性强化：</span><span color="#ff9672">火抗+60%，其他抗性+30%</span><span>，并且全身变亮；该效果持续到其施放</span><span color="#dd4a04">「羽飞刃」</span><span>技能后，或被携带有</span><span color="#dd4a04">「噬骸能量块·火」</span><span>的玩家命中后失效。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
